    "Moreover, the spatiotemporal features of the model were extracted by combining CNNs and LSTM networks.",
    "Then, by visualizing and examining typical forecasts, maps of student's activities, and feature importance, the DL model was described.",
    "The experimental results demonstrated that the combined CNN-LSTM outperformed the baseline LSTM and ML models in the early prediction cases.",
    "Early in the sixth week, the suggested technique correctly predicted student learning performance, with an accuracy of 91%.",
